{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took like one of these things that had like four compartments in it, and then I put all the empty ones back into this carry-all, and I carry it back.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes they left some food in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I could eat it, you know, which was very, you know, much appreciated, to say the least.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this one particular time, I was sitting with my legs hanging out of the lookout tower, and my back towards the soldier who was eating inside the lookout tower.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started a conversation with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, where are you from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I'm Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, how come you speak German?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, well, I've studied a little bit of a German in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I learned here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, what about your father?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where is your father?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, my father is in the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't say a work camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said my father is an officer in the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, the Hungarian army?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, that's right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I thought he was now interested in me, because, you know, my father wasn't that different than him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was relaxed and at ease.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And suddenly, I sense him coming up in back of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I turned to look at him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was a horrible look in his eye, like a glee in his eye.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I got scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I realized that he didn't have anything good in his mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And how old was he about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was probably late '20s, early '30s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, he even told me he's a father too, and he has children, and all this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was totally relaxed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
